{
  "stem": "9943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We used to go to, to swim, to, to, to spend some time on the beach.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he will-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Zonya ?] used to also come to that beach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I met him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I met a number of-- plenty of students.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then he went to Warsaw, that [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Zonya ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was looking for a job-- couldn't find a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He'd been graduated, graduated as an engineer, couldn't find a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we met and started to go out together with him and, and [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Marek ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That's the one that brought my Franka, my little sister, to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to spend a lot of time together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whenever there was time, we used to go to concerts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go in the evenings sometimes to, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to theater, so whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Around-- since you are interested in-- particularly in the issues of Jewishness, there was more and more felt that anti-Semitism was growing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in addition to that, as time went on, some people from Germany came to Poland because of what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then of course, one heard enough about--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about the time-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm still-- if I'm still a student, it means before '35.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's, that's the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We got married in '37-- with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was in Warsaw for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was-- he couldn't find a job in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally we found a job in Katowice, in Slask.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That-- it's Silesia, if you know where that is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, I graduated-- I graduated in 1936.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was supposed to graduate in 1935.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
